{{Quote|Okay, buddy, your funeral. Down Palpatine Boulevard about a kilometer, hang a left, and three blocks onto Imperium.|An individual gives directions to the Imperial Message Center|<ref name="RPG">[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game (first edition)|''Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game'']]</ref>}}
'''Palpatine Boulevard''' was a roadway over a [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometer]] long located three blocks away from [[Imperium]]. An individual once asked for directions to the [[Imperial Message Center]], and was given the directions via Palpatine Boulevard and Imperium.<ref name="RPG" />

